01:09:23,100 --> 01:09:24,739
Put your stuff down,
we ordered pizza, okay?

898
01:09:24,820 --> 01:09:25,979
Wow.

899
01:09:26,500 --> 01:09:28,699
He's very focused on family.

900
01:09:28,780 --> 01:09:34,419
Whether I complain that he's not
or he's not, he really is.

901
01:09:34,500 --> 01:09:37,779
I think that's one of, maybe,

902
01:09:38,780 --> 01:09:43,579
a greatest criticism
and maybe why he withdraws from me

903
