01:10:22,860 --> 01:10:25,179
-Does that count as a point?
-No.

912
01:10:27,260 --> 01:10:29,459
Oh, 3-0.

913
01:10:43,820 --> 01:10:46,379
Okay, thank you very much.
I'll speak to you soon.

914
01:10:46,460 --> 01:10:48,419
I've got to call Robbo.

915
01:10:48,980 --> 01:10:52,139
We just got a gig in Japan. I'm serious, man.

916
01:10:53,260 --> 01:10:56,739
Fucking right. Okay, I'll speak to you after.
