and he's invited us to play

920
01:11:06,340 --> 01:11:08,539
in this massive show in Tokyo.

921
01:11:08,900 --> 01:11:11,739
See, everything turns into something else.

922
01:11:12,180 --> 01:11:15,739
You get on the phone, and then,
all of a sudden, now we're busy.

923
01:11:32,260 --> 01:11:35,739
It feels like an incredible force
of dj vu going on.

924
01:11:35,820 --> 01:11:39,139
I feel like I've lived this moment
for sure before.

925
01:11:39,220 --> 01:11:43,979
Last time I was here, I was in my 20s.
It's really hard to believe that,

926
01:11:44,060 --> 01:11:47,619
fuck, a quarter of a century is gone
since I was last here.

927
01:12:34,900 --> 01:12:37,299
It's good to be back,
but I find out from the promoter

928
01:12:37,380 --> 01:12:39,699
that we're on at 11:35 a.m.

929
01:12:43,060 --> 01:12:48,099
I came all this distance, did all...
Everything that it took to get here

930
01:12:48,180 --> 01:12:51,979
and now what am I worried about?
Is anybody going to show up?

931
01:12:53,580 --> 01:12:56,019
I've been in a situation where

932
